        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3213889604" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8783654005560106563">I have to admit that the first half of this book left me wondering why all my friends loved it. Poor Valancy was not really even a sympathetic character only pathetic. Then her bitterness was so profound I found it disturbing and even sadder. The second half of the book is the reason it is so well-loved. <br/>Quite a diversion and quite fun, although I still think her family was a little overdrawn. <br/>Valancy gets her sabbath rest in a cabin in the woods. Let us all embrace our sabbaths with such joy.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


