<div id="review_3326711520" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3326711520" />
    <a title="Virginie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/10014356-virginie"><img alt="Virginie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1643464136p2/10014356.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3326711520?book_show_action=true">Jul 10, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Virginie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Virginie" href="/user/show/10014356-virginie">Virginie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/35126039-the-blue-castle">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10014356-virginie?shelf=romance">romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10014356-virginie?shelf=drama">drama</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3326711520" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer859725769472980030">Didn&apos;t think I would like this book this much! There were some flaws, but it definitely put me in a good mood.<br/><br/>Full review to come<br/><br/>4.5 rounded up</span>
  <span id="freeText859725769472980030" style="display:none">Didn't think I would like this book this much! There were some flaws, but it definitely put me in a good mood.<br /><br />Full review to come<br /><br />4.5 rounded up</span>
  <a data-text-id="859725769472980030" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

